{"tid":1000637,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"實體化出書！《你聽說過嗎？聖地牙哥鬼屋》","createTime":"2019-01-29T14:12:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-29T17:52:45.000Z","uid":116322,"like":8,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b24341f397a0c748a4b0fd1677b91775b3159568","tid":1000637,"uid":116322,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T14:12:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/01/29/210146_c229227e1f8e208c6f2770d4e1d61e0d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F01%2F29%2F210146_c229227e1f8e208c6f2770d4e1d61e0d.png&h=6b03bd0c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n終於可以告訴大家，<br />\n鬼屋首部曲出版成書了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n感謝你們的支持，尤其提過：<br />\n「以後唔敢食炸雞同肉醬」<br />\n「好驚但又想睇落去」<br />\n每個留言，都激起我繼續寫下去的衝勁，<br />\n當然某部份原因，是我有用文字來虐待你們的癖好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n沒有你們，我可能無法寫完這個故事，<br />\n更遑論出版成書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n感謝點子出版社的賞識，<br />\n還有笑稱讀這書可以減低食慾，有助減肥的編輯姐姐。<br />\n網絡小說何其多，<br />\n你們在茫茫文章中找到這個故事，<br />\n甚至提出將它出版成書，<br />\n對我來說十分難得，簡直是完成了我的夢想。<br />\n<br />\n《你聽說過嗎？聖地牙哥鬼屋》將在這幾天內，<br />\n於各大書店陸續上架，<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />誠邀各位領養回家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n簽名版亦很快在網店發售：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ideapublication.com/products\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ideapublication.com%2Fproducts&d=2pBoyAcJJfm%2FTk9I6oZxMJWZRx3LGI3v3d3gAfzxhEk%3D&h=833dcac7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ideapublication.com/products</a><br />\n<br />\n不妨趁新年幾日連假，<br />\n挑戰一下感官極限吧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>facebook: 橘子綠茶</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/greenizmstory/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgreenizmstory%2F&d=2pBoyAcJJfm%2FTk9I6oZxMJWZRx3LGI3v3d3gAfzxhEk%3D&h=3c19428c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/greenizmstory/</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>ig: greenizmstory</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/greenizmstory/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fgreenizmstory%2F&d=2pBoyAcJJfm%2FTk9I6oZxMJWZRx3LGI3v3d3gAfzxhEk%3D&h=b6c44ed7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/greenizmstory/</a>"},{"pid":"bca43aeca162215432ecce7bbb90f09439d117c9","tid":1000637,"uid":40470,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T14:14:42.000Z","msg":"杯葛左樓主<br />\n<br />\n出版商我知你有睇post<br />\n<br />\n我話你知你蝕硬"},{"pid":"c4e5eb87d36ba07e999e5cf8eccb988a9891ffc3","tid":1000637,"uid":153615,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T14:18:48.000Z","msg":"出版社出咗圖但無講係咩事，原來係你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2bbf8d9e08245629182402ca93c1dd8add70292","tid":1000637,"uid":170630,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T14:26:21.000Z","msg":"女人真好，只要po啲J圖出黎就可以做作家"},{"pid":"de31d99b972b568b15ebeb9e627a2a25e17a5c4a","tid":1000637,"uid":171139,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T14:48:30.000Z","msg":"點子出版搞乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 呢一兩年d書愈黎愈唔掂<br />\n好似搵唔到書出咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲有大把好故可以揀都唔揀"},{"pid":"557a0c873bee999d632788e5aa21ae146a32c482","tid":1000637,"uid":153615,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T17:52:45.000Z","msg":"樓主我支持你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}